KQL Query to remove all suricata specific signatures: 

NOT suricata.eve.alert.signature:SURICATA* 

KQL Query to show only internal traffic: 

source.address:(172.16.* OR 192.168.* OR 10.*) 

KQL Query to show only external traffic: 

NOT source.address:(10.* OR 172.16.* OR 192.168.*) 

KQL Query to show netflow view into large uploads, SYN-scan, null scans, and unusually high port traffic to foreign countries: 

suricata.eve.event_type:"flow" 

AND clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) 

AND NOT destination.address:(172.16.* OR 192.168.* OR 10.*) 

AND ( 

     suricata.eve.flow.bytes_toserver > 1000000 

  OR ( 

       suricata.eve.flow.pkts_toserver < 3  

   AND suricata.eve.flow.protocol:"TCP" 

     ) 

  OR tcp.tcp_flags:0x00 

  OR ( 

       suricata.eve.flow.dest_port > 1024  

   AND NOT destination.geo.country:"US" 

     ) 

) 

 

Base Filter for Netflow Logs: 

suricata.eve.event_type:flow and clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) 

High Uploads (Potential Exfil): 
           suricata.eve.event_type:flow and 

clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) and 

suricata.eve.flow.bytes_toserver > 10000000 

Small Connections (Potential Scanning): 

suricata.eve.event_type:flow and 

clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) and 

suricata.eve.flow.pkts_toserver < 3 

Flows that triggered Alerts: 

suricata.eve.event_type:flow and 

clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) and 

suricata.eve.flow.alerted: true 

Long Duration Connections: 

suricata.eve.event_type:flow and 

clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) and 

suricata.eve.flow.age > 3600 

Timed Out Flows: 

suricata.eve.event_type:flow and 

clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) and 

suricata.eve.flow.reason: "timeout" 

Base Filter for DNS Logs: 

suricata.eve.event_type:dns and clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) 

Suspicious Top Level Domain (TLD) Super-Filter: 

suricata.eve.event_type:dns and 

clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) and 

suricata.eve.dns.rrname: ( 

  *.xyz or *.top or *.gq or *.tk or *.ml or *.cf or 

  *.club or *.online or *.site or *.store or *.click or 

  *.work or *.cam or *.bid or *.men or *.loan or 

  *.trade or *.space or *.win or *.buzz or *.press or 

  *.cn or *.ru or *.su or *.by or *.ir or *.kp or 

  *.zip or *.mov 

) 

Dynamic DNS Providers: 

suricata.eve.event_type:dns and 

clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) and 

suricata.eve.dns.rrname: (*.duckdns.org or *.no-ip.com or *.dyn.*) 

External DNS Resolvers: 

suricata.eve.event_type:dns and 

clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) and 

not destination.address: ("10.*" or "172.16.*" or "192.168.*") 

Queries with Long Subdomains (Domain Generation Algorithms or Exfil): 

suricata.eve.event_type:dns and 

clientID:("<clientID 1>" OR "<clientID 2>" ) and 

Suricata.eve.dns.rrname: *.*.*.*

Alerts with malicious or suspicious content minus false positives:

suricata.eve.alert.signature:* AND suricata.eve.alert.signature : ("*MALWARE*" OR "*TROJAN*" OR "*VIRUS*" OR "*BACKDOOR*" OR "*BOTNET*" OR "*EXPLOIT*" OR "*SHELLCODE*" OR "*INJECTION*" OR "*C2*" OR "*COMMAND AND CONTROL*" OR "*METERPRETER*" OR "*EMOTET*" OR "*QAKBOT*" OR "*TRICKBOT*" OR "*ICEDID*" OR "*DRIDEX*" OR "*AGENT TESLA*" OR "*RAT*" OR "*REMOTE ACCESS*" OR "*REVERSE SHELL*" OR "*EXECUTION*" OR "*DLL INJECTION*"

) AND NOT suricata.eve.alert.signature:(SURICATA* OR "ET MALWARE Windows qwinsta Microsoft Windows DOS prompt command exit OUTBOUND" OR "ET INFO EXE IsDebuggerPresent (Used in Malware Anti-Debugging)")



User agent search exclusion filter to get rid of known benign user agents and a couple benign domains:

suricata.eve.http.http_user_agent:* AND NOT suricata.eve.http.http_user_agent: (

  "Windows-Update-Agent*" OR "downloader*" OR "OUTLOOK*" OR "libdnf*" OR "Yealink*" OR "HIP*" OR "GoogleUpdater*" OR "Debian*" OR "urlgrabber*" OR "DLNADOC*" OR "Mozilla*" OR "HTTP Image Reader" OR "Designjet*" OR "Auvik*" OR "HiIpcam*" OR "aws-sdk-cpp*" OR "NetworkCTS" OR "CaptiveNetworkSupport*" OR "Netflix*" OR "NESSUS*" OR "Nessus*" OR "FileTransport*" OR "SeaPort*" OR "Roku*" OR "Microsoft-CryptoAPI*" OR "AutodeskSync*" OR "WebLink*" OR "Blackbox Exporter/0.26.0" OR "AVG Antivirus" OR "Gibbon*" OR "Rain Bird/LNKSS" OR "Microsoft NCSI" OR "Microsoft-CryptoAPI/10.0" OR "fwupd" OR "AirControl Agent v1.0" OR "Microsoft-Delivery-Optimization/10.0" OR "Microsoft-Delivery-Optimization/10.1" OR "Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 6.2; WOW64; Trident/7.0; .NET4.0C; .NET4.0E; .NET CLR 2.0.50727;NET CLR 3.0.30729; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; Zoom 3.6.0)" OR "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:140.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/140.0" OR "cpprestsdk/2.9.0" OR "log-c-lite_0.1.0" OR "Windows-Update-Agent/10.0.10011.16384 Client-Protocol/2.0" OR "Windows-Update-Agent/1407.2505.15022.0 Client-Protocol/2.90" OR "Windows-Update-Agent/10.0.10011.16384 Client-Protocol/2.51" OR "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64; Trident/7.0; rv:11.0) like Gecko" OR "WSDAPI" OR "Microsoft Office/16.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Microsoft Word 16.0.18827; Pro)") AND NOT suricata.eve.http.hostname.keyword : ("*.meraki.com" OR "download.comodo.com" OR "*.avcdn.net" OR "*.voiceinteraction.pt")



 
